<subSubSection pageId="152" pageNumber="913" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="152.[1395,2606,2766,3470]" pageId="152" pageNumber="913">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1397,1753,3240,3273]" pageId="152" pageNumber="913">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Near Threatened on The IUCN Red List. The 
<collectingCountry box="[1396,1493,3279,3312]" name="Taiwan" pageId="152" pageNumber="913">Taiwan</collectingCountry>
Tube-nosed Bat has a relatively restricted range. It may be affected by deforestation, although this is no longer carried outto a significant degree on the higher elevations of 
<collectingCountry box="[1510,1611,3358,3391]" name="Taiwan" pageId="152" pageNumber="913">Taiwan</collectingCountry>
. The species has been regionally redlisted in 
<collectingCountry box="[2250,2334,3358,3391]" name="China" pageId="152" pageNumber="913">China</collectingCountry>
as endangered.
</paragraph>
